summary: Hosted Control Plane end-of-life upgrade has been initiated
description: To ensure your cluster remains secure and has all critical updates, Red Hat automatically upgraded your cluster running the end-of-life version ${VERSION} to the next supported OpenShift minor version. Your attention may be required if this impacts cluster components or workloads. See this documentation for more information: https://docs.redhat.com/en/documentation/red_hat_openshift_service_on_aws/4/html/introduction_to_rosa/policies-and-service-definition#rosa-minor-versions_rosa-hcp-life-cycle.
